citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 1020 on
22-Jun-17. We went to the house and knocked on the door. No one answered. I honked my car horn. I called the
licensee by phone and left a message. I did not receive a call back. We waited 30 minutes and then left the
property.
End of report.
Additional Inspectors
Sime Debra, Veterinary Medical Officer

narrative:
2.126(b)                    REPEAT
ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 1020 on
22-Jun-17.  We went to the house and knocked on the door.  No one answered.  I honked my car horn.  I called the
licensee by phone and left a message.  I did not receive a call back.  We waited 30 minutes and then left the
property.
End of report.
Additional Inspectors
Sime Debra, Veterinary Medical Officer
